summary: An ordinance relating to an offer to sell to, and providing for the purchase by, the city of certain property in the NE 1/4 of the SE 1/4 of Section 35, Township 26 North, Range 3 E. W. M., except the East 30 feet for street and except the South 160 feet thereof, in King County, Washington, for park and playfield purposes and making an appropriation from Seattle Park Bonds 1948 Fund therefor.
committee: Finance and Parks and Public Grounds
